---
description: Go conventions (service-local)
globs: "**/*.go"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Go

- Domain: `internal/user/`, `internal/auth/` — model, repository, service
- Transport: `internal/app/api/identity/`
- External clients: `internal/adapter/`
- Wiring: `cmd/<service>/app/run.go` only
- `make lint` / `make test` from service root
